the interim stage last year. After administrative expenses of Pounds 66,000
(Pounds 52,000) and tax Pounds 6,000 (Pounds 12,000), loss retained was
Pounds 29,000 (Pounds 61,000 profit). Losses per share were 0.29p (0.61p
earnings).
