FT  21 DEC 93 / Observer: Changing places
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
What better symbol of the yawning gap between commercial and investment
banks? Having reported that Goldman Sachs' partners are each to get a
Dollars 5m share of the profits this year, Chase Manhattan, the
Rockefellers' old family bank, has just announced its Christmas bonus.
