day off work next year and Dollars 300 extra pocket money. Admittedly,
Chase's largesse is spread around all of its 34,000 employees and not just
confined to 161 fat cats, as is the case with Goldman. Even so, Chase is
only handing out the equivalent of two Goldman partners' bonuses.
