<TEXT>
The Financial Times of December 16 incorrectly quoted Mr Nikolaus Boemcke,
secretary general of the European Banking Federation, as implying that
financial services and shipping had been excluded from the Uruguay Round
agreement on global trade liberalisation. In fact, both sectors are included
in the agreement. Further talks are continuing to settle outstanding
differences in these areas.
